@startuml caching-strategy
!theme plain

title Caching Strategy untuk HR Data

rectangle "Mail Service" as MS
rectangle "Local Cache\n(Redis/Caffeine)" as Cache
rectangle "HR REST API\n(Kepegawaian)" as HR

MS --> Cache
Cache --> HR

note bottom of Cache
  Employee: 5-15 min TTL
  Position/Org: 30-60 min TTL
  Invalidation: event-driven (phase 2)
end note

@enduml
